<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="tradition-n">tradition <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /trə'dɪʃn/    美 /trə'dɪʃn/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>传统；风俗：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The tradition of the Dragon Boat Festival started more than 2,000 years ago. 
端午节的传统始于两千多年前。</p><footer>北师大① – 3</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>There’s a <strong><em>_</em></strong>_(传统) in our office that when it’s somebody’s birthday, they bring in a cake for us all to share. 
  （2011 山东改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. tradition  </p></div>